Class Document

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.service.model.GenericModel

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreateDocumentResponse, GetDocumentResponse, UpdateDocumentResponse

    public class Document
extends GenericModel
    A Document contains the processing status and notices, if any, for a document in the index. It does not return the document itself.
    See Also:
    to see how to fetch the actual document content.
